{"tid":2199864,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人老母講野好靈","createTime":"2020-09-12T13:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:46:28.000Z","uid":200305,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c83ea5fae530ddfde6157c5b98d1a27dc28e4632","tid":2199864,"uid":200305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"先唔講其他野 佢睇人好準好靈<br />\n<br />\n成日啲朋友上嚟坐陣 見咗冇十分鐘<br />\n佢已經講得出對方係啲乜性格<br />\n連人地啲口頭禪同習慣都估到差唔多<br />\n<br />\n不過最痴線係佢講我啲野勁靈<br />\n小學佢話我成日跑一定會跌斷骨<br />\n不出一個月真係斷咗手骨 醫咗兩個月<br />\n<br />\n有一期佢話我飲食唔好會生皮膚病<br />\n冇幾耐真係有牛皮癬 到大學先好返<br />\n<br />\n早兩日佢冇神神話我就嚟有腸胃炎<br />\n第二日朝早即刻奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘔到啱啱先停<br />\n<br />\n好心佢出少句聲當幫忙 唔好成日燈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb493b16dfe663c21b89b8ab288bbcd5bc1e09a","tid":2199864,"uid":126226,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"睇得人多同咁岩啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680cd8d0535491470a74ad208c161f83051e8619","tid":2199864,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9638a2b47322329f3b033454176e91695f75b678","tid":2199864,"uid":227951,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:39:49.000Z","msg":"前面都有跡可尋<br />\n最後個段⋯⋯無神神講得出？佢做算命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8492b01ed4fb4c20f704ac1afaf3dfa7884e23","tid":2199864,"uid":90660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"伯母係預言家"},{"pid":"a5ea34dc194cd4f9748136dd559fd7127ea2ab7e","tid":2199864,"uid":200305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9638a2b47322329f3b033454